OL,5, The Education Authority (EA) has been  
OL,6, asked to model cuts of up to 10% of its
OL,7, 2023/24 budget.                        
OL,9,FBBC News NI understands the Department 
OL,10,Fof Education has asked the authority to
OL,11,Fassess the potential impact of cuts of 
OL,12,F3%, 5% and 10%.                        
OL,14,FThe Education Authority is responsible 
OL,15,Ffor spending the bulk of the #2.5bn    
OL,16,Feducation budget.                      
OL,18,FCuts of up to 10% could mean it has to 
OL,19,Ffind hundreds of millions pounds worth 
OL,20,Fof savings.                            
